message.en_US: Welcome, Seeker, to the \c[3]Global Quest Hub\c[0].
message.pt_BR: Bem-vinda, Seeker, ao \c[3]Centro de Missões Global\c[0].
message.ja_JP:
探索者さん、ようこそ
\c[3]グローバル・クエストハブ\c[0]へ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.ko_KR: \c[3]전체 퀘스트 허브\c[0]에 오신 것을 환영합니다, 시커.<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/07]
message.zh_CN: 探索者，欢迎来到\c[3]全球任务中心\c[0]。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]

message.en_US: Here you can find the \c[3]Global Quest Board\c[0] listing \c[3]available quests in all of Shadoon\c[0]!
message.pt_BR: Aqui você encontra o \c[3]Quadro de Missões Globais\c[0] listando as \c[3]missões disponíveis em toda o Shadoon\c[0]!
message.de_DE: Hier findest du das \c[3]Globale Schwarze Brett\c[0], das \c[3]alle verfügbaren Quests in ganz Shadoon\c[0] auflistet!
message.ja_JP:
これは\c[3]シャドゥーン全域のクエスト\c[0]が
載っている\c[3]グローバル・クエスト掲示板\c[0]です！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/03/05]
message.ko_KR: 이곳에서는 \c[3]샤둔 전역에서 이용 가능한 퀘스트\c[0]가 적힌 \c[3]전체 퀘스트 게시판\c[0]을 볼 수 있습니다!<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/03/05]
message.zh_CN: 这里的\c[3]全球任务板\c[0]罗列着\c[3]全沙德隆的所有可用任务\c[0]!<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/03/05]

text.en_US: Sitting on tables is the best!
text.de_DE: Auf Tischen zu sitzen ist das Beste!
text.ja_JP: 一緒にテーブルに座ろうぜ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]
新しい眺めを楽しもう！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]

text.en_US: Together let's spread the joy of \c[3]sitting on tables\c[0]!
text.pt_BR: Juntos vamos espalhar a alegria de \c[3]sentar em mesas\c[0]!
text.de_DE: Verbreiten wir gemeinsam die Freude am \c[3]Tischsitzen\c[0]!
text.ja_JP:
\c[3]テーブルの上に座る\c[0]喜びの輪を
みんなで広げよう！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]
text.ko_KR: 모두 함께 \c[3]테이블 위에 앉는\c[0] 기쁨을 전파합시다!<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/16]
text.zh_CN: 让我们一起分享\c[3]坐桌子\c[0]的愉悦！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/19]

text.en_US: Please return the tables to their original positions!
text.pt_BR: Por favor, devolva as mesas às suas posições originais!
text.de_DE: Stellt die Tische bitte wieder an ihren ursprünglichen Platz!
text.ja_JP:
テーブルを全部、元あった場所に
戻してくれ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]

text.en_US: Ugh...\. we'll so get into trouble for this.
text.pt_BR: Ahr...\. nós vamos ter problemas por isso.
text.de_DE: Örks...\. Das wird so was von Ärger geben.
text.ja_JP: ふぅ...\.困ったことになったな。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]
text.zh_CN: 呃...\.我们会惹上大麻烦的。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/19]

text.en_US: The NPCs...\. they just keep sitting there.\. It's kind of sad.
text.pt_BR: Os NPCs...\. eles continuam sentados lá.\. É meio triste.
text.de_DE: Diese NPCs...\. bleiben einfach weiter sitzen.\. Wirkt fast schon etwas traurig.
text.ja_JP:
NPCのヤツら...\.こんな感じでずっと
座ってんだな。\.なんか悲しい。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/03/05]
text.ko_KR: NPC들이...\. 그냥 저렇게 계속 앉아 있어.\. 왠지 슬프다.<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/03/05]
text.zh_CN: 那些NPC...\.只会这样坐着。\.有点可怜。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/03/05]

text.en_US: To be fair, they probably didn't expect players to find a way to move the tables.
text.pt_BR: Para ser justo, eles provavelmente não esperavam que os jogadores encontrassem uma forma de mover as mesas.
text.de_DE: Um fair zu sein, haben sie wahrscheinlich nicht erwartet, dass der Spieler einen Weg findet, die Tische zu bewegen.
text.ja_JP:
少なくとも、プレイヤーがテーブルを
移動できる方法が見つかると予想
できなかったんだろうなぁ...<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/03/05]
text.ko_KR: 플레이어들이 테이블을 옮길 방법을 찾아낼 줄 몰랐나 봐.<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/03/05]
text.zh_CN: 老实说，他们估计没料到玩家能移动桌子。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/03/05]

text.en_US: I hope they'll patch this soon before the chaos spreads any further.
text.pt_BR: Espero que resolvam isso logo antes que o caos se espalhe ainda mais.
text.de_DE: Ich hoffe, sie patchen das bald, bevor sich das Chaos noch weiter verbreitet.
text.ja_JP:
混乱がこれ以上広がる前に、開発者が
パッチを配信してくれると良いんだけど。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]
text.ko_KR: 더 혼란스러워지기 전에 패치 내 주겠지?<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/16]
text.zh_CN: 希望他们赶紧修复，免得出更多乱子。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/19]

text.en_US: Please return the tables to their original positions!
text.pt_BR: Por favor, devolva as mesas às suas posições originais!
text.de_DE: Stellt die Tische bitte wieder an ihren ursprünglichen Platz!
text.ja_JP:
テーブルを全部、元あった場所に
戻してくれ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]

text.en_US: Man... I don't know.\. Should we really keep sitting here?
text.pt_BR: Cara... não sei.\. Devemos mesmo continuar sentados aqui?
text.de_DE: Ach Mann... Ich weiß nicht.\. Sollen wir hier wirklich sitzen bleiben?
text.ja_JP:
おい…なんだか知らんが。\.ここにずっと
座ってないとダメなのか？<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]
text.ko_KR: 으아... 모르겠다.\. 여기 계속 앉아 있어야 해?<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/16]
text.zh_CN: 呃。\.我们真要一直这么坐着？<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/19]

text.en_US: Someone has to do it, or they'll take back the tables.
text.pt_BR: Alguém tem que fazer isso, ou eles vão pegar as mesas de volta.
text.de_DE: Einer muss es machen, sonst stellen sie die Tische wieder zurück.
text.ja_JP:
誰かが座ってないと、ヤツらがテーブル
片付けるだろ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]
text.ko_KR: 누군가는 앉아 있어야지. 안 그러면 저 사람들이 가져가 버릴 거야.<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/16]
text.zh_CN: 总得有人压着，不然他们就要把桌子弄回去了。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/19]

text.en_US: Don't you want to run the new dungeon?
text.pt_BR: Você não quer começar a nova dungeon?
text.de_DE: Willst du nicht den neuen Dungeon machen?
text.ja_JP: 新しいダンジョンやりたくないか？<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]
text.ko_KR: 새 던전에 가 보고 싶지 않아?<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/16]

text.en_US: Meh. It'll probably be crowded anyway.
text.pt_BR: Meh. Provavelmente vai estar lotado de qualquer forma.
text.de_DE: Nah. Wird wahrscheinlich eh überfüllt sein.
text.ja_JP: 別に。どっちみちめっちゃ混むだろ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]
text.zh_CN: 不想。里面人多的估计跟下饺子似的。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/19]

text.en_US: The dungeon can wait. This is important!
text.pt_BR: A dungeon pode esperar. Isso é importante!
text.de_DE: Der Dungeon kann warten. Das hier ist wichtiger!
text.ja_JP:
ダンジョンは待っててくれる。
これは大切なことだぞ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/09]
text.ko_KR: 던전이 어디 가는 것도 아닌데, 뭐. 그것보단 이게 더 중요해!<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/16]
text.zh_CN: 地牢可以等。这才是最重要的！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/19]
